\tab Magick Effects: This invocation reveals the presence of Chaos in its explicit form. Similar to {\i detect magick}
, it will detect chaos humanoids, beastmen, mutants, and so on, but not humans who are members of Chaos cults. Will not detect an unblessed cult symbol, but does indicate any sort of sacred ground. Detects artifacts and divine instruments of Chaos, whether
 their powers are active or dormant. Not blocked by mundane substances, but a large enough amount of Warpdust, Warpstone, or other Chaos energies will mask smaller amounts of Chaos.\par 
