}\pard\plain \s1\qj \f18\fs28 Grim Resolve\par 
\pard\plain \qj \f16\fs20 Discipline/Level: Runemaster 2 Ritual\par 
Preparation: 1d6+3 rounds\par 
Magick Points: 3 per 10 creatures\par 
Range: Caster\par 
Duration: 1d6+3 hours\par 
Area of Effect: 10 yard radius sphere\par 
